description: The demolition of seven (7) existing garages at Bampton Estate, Bampton Road SE23, to allow for the construction of one (1) part three/part four/part five storey building to provide thirty nine (39) over 55s dwelling units, together with the provision of the relocated ball court, associated landscaping, refuse storage and cycle and car parking.
